<td>
<h2>Overview</h2>
<p>Bika 3 <a class="external-link" href="http://www.vanhunks.com/lowveld1/modjadji1.html">Modjadji,</a> <i>The Rain Queen</i>, is Bika's long awaited upgrade to Plone 4 and SQL</p>
<p>In    the interest of future maintenance and performance, and  facilitating new functionality, the opportunity was used to undertake  significant code restructuring</p>
<h3>Note to Testers</h3>
<p>With this release, please concentrate (and try to break) the LIMS' setup and basic workflow for Samples, Analyses, Analysis Requests and Worksheets. Please do test Analysis profiles, Specifications and Worksheet templates</p>
</td>
<td>
<h2 class="Subheading">Set-up data</h2>
<p>We are finalising standardised  and open XLSX<b> </b>spreadsheets that can be used   to  populate the LIMS with setup data of  your choice. Please contribute standard setup data to guide us    in pre-populating setup data  for each of the Bika branches,  e.g. Water, Health, Interlab, etc.</p>
<h3><a class="internal-link" href="setup-data-in-this-installation">Test data</a></h3>
<p>For the purpose of testing, we use these to populate this   instance with data of uniform   nature for for most setup items, e.g. Analysis specifications,   QC, uncertainties, turn-around time, precision, price   etc. Please see <a class="internal-link" href="setup-data-in-this-installation">Setup data used to configure this installation</a></p>
</td>
<td>
<h2 class="Subheading">Feedback</h2>
<p>Don't hesitate to post questions, comments and suggestions to the Bika mailing lists: Bika <a class="external-link" href="https://groups.google.com/forum/?hl=en#%21forum/bika-design">LIMS design</a>, <a class="external-link" href="http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/bika-users">Users</a> or <a class="external-link" href="http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/bika-developers">Developers</a>. Please log issues in the <a class="external-link" href="http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?func=browse&amp;group_id=145464&amp;atid=762012">public Bika bug tracker</a> at SourceForge.net</p>
<h3>Code repository</h3>
<p>Fresh code is in SVN at <a class="external-link" href="https://bika.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/bika/bika3">https://bika.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/bika/bika3</a></p>
</td>
</tr>
